下學期實驗內容

Part IV
  安培計，伏特計和歐姆計 (The Ammeter, Voltmeter and Ohmmeter)
電流天平 (The Current Balance)
示波器實驗 (Digital Oscilloscope)

演示實驗D: 電、磁學篇 (Demonstrations D)

  Part V
  電位量測 (The Electric Field) 
光的折射、偏振、干涉和繞射(Optical Experiment)

RC與RLC線路 (RC and RLC Circuits)

演示實驗:電磁學與能源篇 (Demonstrations E)

  Part VI
  亥姆霍茲線圈 (Helmholtz Coils)

邁克生干涉儀&密立根油滴實驗(Michelson  interferometer & Millikan oil drop exp.)
原子光譜量度與浦郎克常數 (Atomic spectrum and Planck constant)
演示實驗F:光電與近代物理學篇 (Demonstrations F)


 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 

 



